==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quarry
<hw>Quar"ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>quarre</ets>, OF. <ets>quarr⟦eacute⟧</ets> square, F.
<ets>carr⟦eacute⟧</ets>, from L. <ets>quadratus</ets> square, quadrate,
<ets>quadratum</ets> a square. See <er>Quadrate</er>, and cf.
<er>Quarrel</er> an arrow.]</ety> <def>Same as 1st
<er>Quarrel</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Fairfax.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

