==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Quarry
<hw>Quar"ry</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>quarr⟦eacute⟧</ets>.]</ety> <def>Quadrate; square.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
